.TH IMGMOD-COMPLETION 1 "July 7, 2026" "imgmod 1.1.0"
.SH NAME
imgmod-completion \- Print imgmod shell completion data
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B imgmod completion
\fBcommands\fR
.br
.B imgmod completion
\fBoptions\fR [\fICOMMAND\fR]
.br
.B imgmod completion
\fBbash\fR|\fBzsh\fR|\fBfish\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B imgmod completion
prints command candidates, option candidates, and generated shell completion
scripts for
.BR imgmod (1).

Shell completion scripts call this plugin dynamically, so XDG plugins appear in
completion without regenerating shell files.
.SH TOPICS
.TP
.B bash
Print a Bash completion script.
.TP
.B zsh
Print a Zsh completion script.
.TP
.B fish
Print a Fish completion script.
.TP
.B commands
Print command names, one per line.
.TP
.B options [\fICOMMAND\fR]
Print top-level option names, or option names for \fICOMMAND\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, --help
Show usage help.
.TP
.B \-v, --version
Show the plugin name and version.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Load Bash completion:
.nf
.B source <(imgmod completion bash)
.fi
.TP
Load Zsh completion:
.nf
.B eval "$(imgmod completion zsh)"
.fi
.TP
Load Fish completion:
.nf
.B imgmod completion fish | source
.fi
.TP
Inspect command candidates:
.nf
.B imgmod completion commands
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR imgmod (1)
